/comment/30453","id":"30453","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=gregdek","name":"gregdek","key":"gregdek","accountId":"557058:03f83db3-3217-4d33-ab46-1e156057c13d","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Greg DeKoenigsberg","active":false,"timeZone":"America/New_York"},"body":"Ah. From IRC:\n\n21:19:54 < gregdek> And I guess policies at the \"account\" level is just a bug.\n21:20:04 < gholms> It actually isn't.\n21:20:17 < gregdek> Ah, ok. What's the use case? Because I can't figure it out.\n21:20:44 < gholms> Eucalyptus adds an extension to IAM that allows you do attach quota policies (and only quota policies) to accounts.\n21:21:08 < gholms> Perhaps it should reject account policies that contain non-quota things.\n21:21:19 < jeevan_ullas> yep thats the bug\n21:21:30 < gholms> \\o/\n21:21:31 <@Tybstar> well,i guess it did reject it\n21:21:34 <@Tybstar> didn't it?\n21:21:39 < gholms> Did it?\n21:21:44 <@Tybstar> 20:45 <gregdek> \"Failed to add policy Allow-all: Failed to add policy Allow-all to account 073501631485: Access to the resource is denied\"\n21:21:46  * gholms actually has zero context here\n21:21:50 < gholms> Oh\n21:21:52 < gregdek> Ah, indeed.\n21:21:54 <@Tybstar> but the message is...not clear\n21:21:58 < gregdek> No. :)\n\nSo the problem is that there *is* a use for the \"add policy\" button on the Accounts screen, but *only* if that policy involves quotes.\n\nThe likely resolution: add text in this case that says \"Failed to add policy FooBarBaz to account 123456789: only quota-related policies can be defined at the account level\" or some such.","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=gregdek","name":"gregdek","key":"gregdek","accountId":"557058:03f83db3-3217-4d33-ab46-1e156057c13d","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/152ea15ef67a66fe6a55c0ae34273f55?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26avatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Greg DeKoenigsberg","active":false,"timeZone":"America/New_York"},"created":"2012-07-31T23:33:54.994-0500","updated":"2012-07-31T23:33:54.994-0500"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/14957/comment/38041","id":"38041","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=wenye","name":"wenye","key":"wenye","accountId":"557058:410304ee-1904-4d8c-8ca1-b1148436b5a6","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/b87135ce3de714cf85240f6d40638792?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FavatarId%3D10122%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","2